  "instructions": [
    "In a pan, heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil over medium heat. Fry the onions until crispy.",
    "Set the fried onions aside on a paper towel-lined plate.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine the tamarind paste, fish sauce, lime juice, salt, and pepper. Blend until smooth.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the mixed greens and crispy fried onions.",
    "Slice the prosciutto into thin strips.",
    "Add the sliced prosciutto to the bowl and toss to combine.",
    "Drizzle the tamarind dressing over the salad and toss again.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately."
